<subSubSection id="C3058B8FFF8A0459FF1EFB7FFEC8FA8C" pageId="60" pageNumber="565" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA0D804FF8A0459FF1EFB7FFEC8FA8C" blockId="60.[151,1127,1209,1361]" pageId="60" pageNumber="565">
<emphasis id="B96B0416FF8A0459FF1EFB7FFE8FFB0C" bold="true" box="[151,271,1209,1233]" pageId="60" pageNumber="565">Comment.</emphasis>
Examination of 
<specimenCount id="9D19138DFF8A0459FE36FB7FFDD8FB0F" box="[447,600,1209,1234]" pageId="60" pageNumber="565" type="generic" typeStatus="syntypes">three syntypes</specimenCount>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C1FA387FF8A0459FDF2FB7DFC5FFB0C" authority="Walker, 1873" authorityName="Walker" authorityYear="1873" box="[635,991,1209,1234]" class="Insecta" family="Largidae" genus="Physopelta" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="565" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="apicalis">
<emphasis id="B96B0416FF8A0459FDF2FB7DFCCBFB0F" box="[635,843,1211,1234]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="565">Physopelta apicalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8EA5F5FF8A0459FCDBFB7FFC5FFB0C" author="Walker" box="[850,991,1209,1233]" firstAuthor="Walker" pageId="60" pageNumber="565" refId="ref68837" refString="WALKER F. 1873: Catalogue of the specimens of Heteropterous Hemiptera in the collection of the British Museum. Part VI. Trustees of the British Museum, London, 210 pp." type="book" year="1873">Walker, 1873</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
deposited in BMNH revealed that this species shares a combination of characters placing it rather near the genus 
<taxonomicName id="4C1FA387FF8A0459FE8CFB3DFE3CFACC" authority="Stal, 1870" authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1870" box="[261,444,1272,1298]" class="Insecta" family="Largidae" genus="Iphita" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="565" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B96B0416FF8A0459FE8CFB3DFEC5FACF" box="[261,325,1275,1298]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="565">Iphita</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8EA5F5FF8A0459FEC5FB3EFE3CFACC" author="Stal" box="[332,444,1272,1297]" firstAuthor="Stal" pageId="60" pageNumber="565" pagination="90 - 124" refId="ref67407" refString="STAL C. 1870: Enumeratio Hemipterorum I. Kongliga Svenska Vetenskap-Academiens Handlingar 9 (1): 90 - 124." type="journal article" year="1870">Stål, 1870</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, but also some unique characters (especially the forked process on procoxa) supporting its placement in a separate genus yet to be described (STEHLÍK &amp; KMENT in press).
</paragraph>
